title: Chanel Mini Rectangular Flap Bag
description: Chanel mini rectangular flap bag in light grey diamond-quilted lambskin leather (#29xxxxxx: 2020). Featuring silver-toned hardware, a rear exterior patch pocket, and single chain leather shoulder strap. The CC turn lock closure on front flap opens to a tonal leather interior with patch and zip pockets. Approx dimensions: 20cm(L) x 13cm(H) x 6cm(D), strap drop 58cm. Accompanied by Chanel card and dustbag. With Entrupy Certificate of Authenticity. (Pre-owned)
